*window* *split* *ctrl-W* *ctrl-w* *W*
:[vert] new {file}           opens new vertical window *vertical*
:e {file}                    opens file in current window *:e* *open* *file* *current*
CTRL-W <Arrow-Key>           moves the cursor to another window in the direction of the arrow key
CTRL-W K	                 Move the current window to be at the very top, using the full width of the screen
CTRL-W H	                 Move the current window to be at the far left, using the full height of the screen
CTRL-W T	                 Move the current window to a new tab page
